/tmp/G2S/
# Local shared runtime root used by the default server storage path
# Includes structured runtime sidecars under /tmp/G2S/{logs,warnings,errors,progress,meta}
# Algorithm PARAM logging now covers runtime flags such as -wPO; logs remain disposable runtime artifacts.
# README.md and DOCUMENTATION.md describe the stateless cursor-based log polling model; no runtime cursor files should be tracked in-repo.
# Reporting-probe smoke tests are expected to create only disposable /tmp/G2S runtime artifacts.
# The checked-in probe examples intentionally do not suppress fatal interface exceptions.

